      <hedline>
        <hl1>MITSUBISHI MOTORS IS FINED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Miki Tanikawa</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Tanikawa, Miki</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Tokyo court orders Mitsubishi Motors to pay fine of 4 million yen, or about $37,000, maximum penalty, for failing to report repairs of defective automobiles to Transport Ministry and failing to disclose cases to the public; company eventually recalled 620,000 cars and trucks (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A Tokyo court has ordered Mitsubishi Motors to pay a fine of 4 million yen, or about $37,000, the maximum penalty, for failing to report repairs of defective automobiles to the Transport Ministry and failing to disclose the cases to the public. The company eventually recalled 620,000 cars and trucks.</p>
        <p>Miki Tanikawa</p>
      </block>
